#187;I will raise them up a Prophet...&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=15'>Deu 18:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=18'>Deu 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=3&verse=23'>Act 3:23</a> <br/> - Psa. 2:1, &#187;Why do the heathen rage...&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=2&verse=2'>Psa 2:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=4&verse=26'>Act 4:26</a> <br/> - Psa. 2:7, &#187;Thou art my Son...&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=2&verse=7'>Psa 2:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=33'>Act 13:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=1&verse=5'>Heb 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=5&verse=5'>Heb 5:5</a> <br/> - Psa. 8:2, &#187;Out of the mouth of babes and sucklings...&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=8&verse=2'>Psa 8:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=16'>Mat 21:16</a> <br/> - Psa. 8:4, &#187;What is man, that thou are mindful of him...&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=8&verse=6'>Psa 8:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=2&verse=8'>Heb 2:8</a> <br/> - Psa. 16:8, &#187;I have set the Lord always before me...&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=16&verse=11'>Psa 16:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=28'>Act 2:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=31'>Act 2:31</a> <br/> - Psa. 16:10, &#187;Neither wilt thou suffer thine Holy One...&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=16&verse=10'>Psa 16:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=35'>Act 13:35</a> <br/> - Psa. 22:1